Meeting Notes - # Summary
The project kickoff meeting was held on November 15, 2023. During the meeting, the project goals and timeline were reviewed, initial tasks were assigned to team members, and potential risks and mitigation strategies were discussed.

# Action Items
1. Create project documentation
2. Set up development environment
3. Schedule weekly check-ins

# Decisions Made
- The project goals and timeline were finalized.
- Initial tasks were assigned to team members.
- Potential risks and mitigation strategies were discussed.

# Next Steps
1. The team will create project documentation to provide a clear understanding of the project.
2. The development environment will be set up to ensure efficient and effective work.
3. Weekly check-ins will be scheduled to track progress and address any issues or concerns.
